      <para id="id10754629">Listen to the recording of the <emphasis effect="italics">Ritual Healing Music</emphasis> from Malawi which your educator will play you. </para>
      <list id="id4325314" list-type="bulleted">
        <item> How many music parts do you hear? </item>
        <item>Can you identify each part?  </item>
      </list>
      <para id="id4474158"/>
      <list id="id3994268" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Independence of the parts.</item>
        <item>Independence with regard to rhythm.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id4322085"/>
      <para id="id4114203"/>
      <para id="id4114207">In African music each part is rhythmically independent from the other, but a unit is still formed. Follow the educator's instructions:</para>
